{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_13_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 河童の悪霊なのかも",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ロケ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんは。月のテンペストの白石沙季です\n私は今、東北地方のある場所に来ています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.4090480168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "この辺りには昔から悪霊伝説なる言い伝えがある\nようで、今回はその調査に向かいたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.2864405633
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。ロケには慣れているとはいえ\nこうも周りが真っ暗だと緊張してしまいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "オープニング撮影お疲れ様\nこれから場所を変えて撮影を再開するみたいだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9210438491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.3210433324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "目的地は外れにある廃病院でしたよね\n何事もなければいいのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.9654198965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ドッキリだし、必ず何かは起こるんだけどな）\n（しかも、千紗が台本に書いた通りの内容が）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ただ、怖さを抑えるように頼んだせいか）\n（どうも斜め上の内容になってしまっていたけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.4654198965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季がドッキリを見破れるのか、検証も兼ねているが）\n（逆にあからさま過ぎてすぐにバレないか心配だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.0654198965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "あの、さっきからずっと神妙な顔をしていますが\nどうかしたんですか？　何か気になることでも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、沙季が気付かないか心配というか……\nもちろん、最終的には気付いてほしいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6000025432,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10466.664123499995,
          "startTime": 87.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9933.3307901,
          "startTime": 86.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.2306603116
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.2666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なんの話ですか？　も、もしかして、何かいるとか……\nあ……い、移動するみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうみたいだな。……沙季、頑張ってくれ\n俺は近くで見守っているぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5835675765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.8930442813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなに含みのある言い方をするんですか？\nうぅ、{user}さん霊感でもあるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.766671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.2955402378
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.2955402378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら伝説によりますと、多くの悪霊達が\nこの奥の廃病院を根城にしているそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0000066122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.5935220723
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.3000066122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "伝説といえば、普通は祠とかの気もしますが……\nあ、スタッフさんによると割と最近の伝説だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3000066122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.2692363744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　噂では河童の悪霊も住んでいる！？\n妖怪の悪霊……よく分かりませんが、強そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.0653816229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "やはり相撲の勝負を挑んでくるんでしょうか\nそもそも悪霊って触れるのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（早速、千紗の洗礼を受けているな……）\n（ただ、真面目な分言われたまま信じているみたいだが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 151.5427512175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "人里離れた森だからか、とても静かです\n聞こえてくるのは虫の声ぐらいのもの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8000066122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "自然豊かで、空には満天の星空……\nこんな所に悪霊が住み着いているなんて信じられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.2578907019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、霊感があれば何か分かるのでしょうか\n同じグループの芽衣ちゃんは霊感があるそうですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.049717713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "でもその分、私なりに、この地域に伝わる\n悪霊伝説について、事前に調べておいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.733321635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "この土地には古くから鷹狩の文化があり\n今では形を変えて、お祭りに取り入れられており――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.433321635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 191.4302414902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（そろそろ、千紗の仕掛けの一つ目が発動するな）\n（さて、どんな反応をするか……）",
